}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device is using MT7601U (MT7601UN).
"48DNUR28.SGA" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :"48DNUR28.0GA" is silkscreened on some production model boards.
There is a MAC label with a 00:6B:9E ('''[[VIZIO]]''') OUI on the board in the FCC external photos.
Some units have U.FL connectors.
This module appears to be used with the... *Vizio E320i-B2, E480i-B2, M471i-A2, M492i-B2, and probably others
